{"id": "test-00881", "text": "A police spokesman said two youths believed to be supporters of President Nelson Mandela's African National Congress (ANC) had been killed when unknown gunmen opened fire at the rural settlement of Izingolweni on KwaZulu-Natal province's south coast on Thursday night.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 74, "end": 88, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Nelson Mandela"}, {"start": 91, "end": 116, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "African National Congress"}, {"start": 118, "end": 121, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "ANC"}, {"start": 198, "end": 209, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "Izingolweni"}, {"start": 213, "end": 226, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "KwaZulu-Natal"}]}
